message.entry: StateSpace property of stateValidator must point to the same state space object as stateSpace.
StateSpace property of StateSampler must point to the same state space object as stateSpace.
Start state is either not valid based on the planner's state validator, or is not finite.
Goal state is either not valid based on the planner's state validator, or is not finite.
Interpolated state must be a row vector with a single state when the interpolation ratio is a scalar.
